<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background-color: #fff;
      margin: 40px auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4caf50;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: white;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .body {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .body p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .confirm-button {
      background-color: #4caf50;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .confirm-button:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #888;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #4caf50;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Confirm Your Email</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hello {{ FullName }},</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining Recruify. To complete your registration, please confirm your email by clicking the button below:</p>
      <a href="{{ ConfirmationLink }}" class="confirm-button">Confirm Account</a>
      <p>If you didnâ€™t sign up, please disregard this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you need assistance, feel free to <a href="https://www.google.com">contact us</a>.</p>
      <p>&copy; 2024 Recruify, All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
